## Additional Notes

### Bhagavad Gita Content
The Bhagavad Gita verses and translations included in this project are from 
public domain sources and traditional Sanskrit texts. We honor the sacred 
nature of these teachings and encourage respectful use.

### Attribution
If you use this project or its concepts in your work, please consider 
acknowledging the source and the spiritual tradition of the Bhagavad Gita.

### Disclaimer
This project is for educational and spiritual learning purposes. The AI-generated 
responses are interpretations based on training data and should not replace 
traditional spiritual guidance or scholarly study of the original texts.